{{[INFO] Executing: cmd.exe /X /C "C:	ools\maven\apache-maven-3.0.5 in\mvn -s C:\Users\BENTAT~1\AppData\Local\Tempelease-settings7104117089287244257.xml clean install --no-plugin-updates --batch-mode -DperformRelease=true}}

While release-finish and hotfix-finish provide parameters to enable this or not, I think it can either be disabled always in this case, or at least parameterized to disable it.

