I'm having trouble getting {{TestPrefTest}} (need to change that name) working. Specifically, the part where it submits the user prefs form.

I've tried all of these, with no success:

{code:java}
client.click("//input[@id='" + gadgetId + "save']");
client.submit("//form[@id='" + gadgetId + "edit']");
